posts.name: 55 South
posts.note: 55 South is an industrial space for inventive Southern comfort eats along with specialty drinks and weekend brunch. You need to order the hot chicken sandwich or the jambalaya. NOTE: They have multiple locations.

posts.name: Dandgure's Classic Southern Cooking
posts.note: Dandgure's Classic Southern Cooking is a long-standing cafeteria-style establishment providing Southern lunch staples in down-home surrounds.

posts.name: Farm House Restaurant
posts.note: Farm House Restaurant serves an all you can eat buffet available every day and catfish buffet on Friday and Saturday. You need to order the Biscuits with chocolate gravy. They even serve frogs legs from the photos I've seen.

posts.name: Peg Leg Porker BBQ
posts.note: Peg Leg Porker BBQ serves pulled pork, ribs, fried pies, and buckets of beer on the patio or in the plain but soulful interior.
